    "Name": "Javelin",
    "Details": "Jalastar Aerospace's newest Javelin variant returns to the classic set-up, upgraded with everything the modern day has to offer. Clan-spec missile racks provide the Javelin's bite, while a locally made 240 XL engine, shared with the Cuirass, delivers additional speed. Jump jets take full advantage of the extra power, delivering leaps of nearly a quarter-kilometer. Finally, head-mounted TAG provides an 'ace in the hole' when supported by artillery or homing missiles. The AFFS is assigning the new Javelins to recon lances containing similarly speedy Stingers and Wasps.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>",
